Key Match Events: Zach Edey contributed four points and two rebounds in the first quarter.
Edey grabbed two offensive rebounds and scored a bank shot in the second quarter.
The Houston Rockets opened the third quarter with a 17-0 run.
Edey scored a layup off a Jake LaRavia pass early in the fourth quarter.
Post-Match Reflections: Grizzlies coach Taylor Jenkins commented on Zach Edey's eagerness to improve after his debut struggles, stating that Edey is in a great head space and is learning a lot.
